column52: Petitions to remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 have been going swimmingly, but more needs to be done! Many want Johnny Depp to be brought back on as Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean, but he does not want that. Instead, this petition seeks to get Justice for Johnny by bringing Johnny into the Justice League! While giving him his own role as a new hero would be in itself a form of redemption for what has been done to him by Amber Heard, giving him her role would make the redemption all the more sweeter. #JusticeforJohnny #JohnnyforJustice
